snippet.title: Police Quest : Swat (1995) FMV game trailer
snippet.description:
RIP Daryl F Gates , the inspiration for this game who died on 16 Apr 2010. 

Shifting from an adventure series to a tactical simulator, SWAT puts you in command of a member on a swat team. Centered around training and then several missions, your adherence to procedure and team work will determine the outcome.
